### Create Sandbox VM with one Allowed Folder

$ /Users/me/Projects/sand/.build/debug/sand create sand-wd-234712 --cpus 2 --memory 1GB
[exit 0]

$ /Users/me/Projects/sand/.build/debug/sand folders add sand-wd-234712 /tmp/sand-working-directory-sand-wd-234712/project rw --as /workspace/project
[exit 0]

$ /Users/me/Projects/sand/.build/debug/sand folders list sand-wd-234712
Host Path	Guest Path	Access Mode
/tmp/sand-working-directory-sand-wd-234712/project	/workspace/project	read-write
[exit 0]


